<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>1. AGGO problem: This is main problem that Wiz tends to death so frequently, I suggest it can patch the survival way for wiz, such as -- improve the teleport setup(fade, shadow step, yonder), all the three are random directions, and that maked the escape more risky.&nbsp; for example: Fade--&gt; teleport backward a distance .&nbsp; Shadow step--&gt; teleport a distance toward the direction you are facing while the casting is completed.&nbsp; Yonder--&gt; teleport to the neighborhood you're targeting in the zone.&nbsp; These is for solution of wiz's survival.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>2. MANA REGEN problem: Just&nbsp;add the regen rate to Familiar line or increase them, or shorten the re-casting time of spell:Harvest and setup the effect to regain 20% max mana. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The above two might make wiz players less complains.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
