<P>1) How does me stunning something add to the groups dps?&nbsp; When I stun something that typically lowers my dps... and in turn lowers the groups dps. And if you're talking about giving a wizard an targeted ae stun.. why?&nbsp; Our stuns are for gater/cheal and defensive purposes</P>
<P>2) Druids have 2!!!! ae roots, maybe you should look at the spell lists again, and just by the fact you didn't know that, prolly means that you've never seen a druid use them, so that tells you how useful those ae roots are...</P>
